# ============================================
# PANDUAN MEMBUAT FIREBASE PROJECT BARU:
# ============================================
# 
# 1. Buka https://console.firebase.google.com
# 2. Klik "Add project" atau "Tambah project"
# 3. Masukkan nama project (contoh: texa-tools-production)
# 4. Aktifkan/nonaktifkan Google Analytics sesuai kebutuhan
# 5. Klik "Create project"
#
# SETUP AUTHENTICATION:
# 1. Di sidebar, klik "Authentication"
# 2. Klik "Get started"
# 3. Enable "Google" sign-in provider
# 4. Enable "Email/Password" sign-in provider
#
# SETUP FIRESTORE:
# 1. Di sidebar, klik "Firestore Database"
# 2. Klik "Create database"
# 3. Pilih mode "Start in production mode" atau "test mode"
# 4. Pilih lokasi server (asia-southeast1 untuk Indonesia)
#
# SETUP REALTIME DATABASE (Optional):
# 1. Di sidebar, klik "Realtime Database"
# 2. Klik "Create database"
# 3. Pilih lokasi server
#
# GET CONFIG:
# 1. Klik gear icon ⚙️ di sidebar > "Project settings"
# 2. Scroll ke "Your apps"
# 3. Klik icon web "</>" untuk register app
# 4. Copy konfigurasi yang ditampilkan
#
